### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/today-sum
@contentType = application/json

### Get all TodaySums
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get TodaySum by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create new TodaySum
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

